                                            </ul>
                                            <a href="" class="btn btn-lg">Đăng kí</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                    <div class="choose_single_pricing_text proffetional_price wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="2s">
                                        <h3>Gói kim cương</h3>
                                        <div class="choose_pricing_text">
                                            <p>Gói câu hỏi này gồm 500 câu hỏi và nhiều mức độ ở mỗi môn học.</p>
